win: +exec autoexec_<game_name> -d3d -r_emulate_gl -heapsize 1572864 -novid -nojoy -nosteamcontroller -nohltv -particles 1 -precachefontchars -nostartupsound -nouserclip -disable_d3d9_hacks -nod3d9ex -limitvsconst
lin: +exec autoexec_<game_name> -gl -heapsize 1572864 -novid -nojoy -nosteamcontroller -nohltv -particles 1 -precachefontchars -nostartupsound -nouserclip -limitvsconst

Change "-heapsize" to amount of memory if game is 64 bit.
